              "text": "For aught Thou dost;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For crosses sore, or paths I cannot see:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But I will trust."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No second causes shall perplex my soul,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Or stay from yielding all to Thy control."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The raging storm I dare not fight alone,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ah, show Thy face!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Say, “It is I!” Thyself to me make known,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ah, show Thy face!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then what care I for darkest depths of woe?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thine arms, O Christ, shall fold me close, I know!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, save me, Lord! Subdue this stubborn will;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, save me, Lord!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spite of all, Thy purposes fulfil"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In me, Oh, Lord;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I yield my self, and all I have and am,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To follow Thee, Thou all redeeming Lamb!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How can I fear? Thou art so near to me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How can I fear?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I hear Thee say, “Believe, and thou shalt see!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How can I fear?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I now believe, and trust Thy mighty power,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To save, to heal, to keep this very hour!"
            }
          ]
        }
